sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (zkLogin)
    participant F as Frontend (Next.js + dapp-kit)
    participant S as Sui Testnet
    participant A as Admin

    A->>S: create_match(AdminCap, fighter_a, fighter_b, lock_ms)
    S-->>F: MatchCreated event
    U->>F: Google OAuth (zkLogin)
    F->>S: mint(MintCap, user_addr) [sponsored]
    S-->>U: Passport (owned, soulbound)
    U->>F: Vote fighter A
    F->>S: vote(match, 0, &passport, clock)
    S-->>F: VoteCast event
    A->>S: settle(AdminCap, match, 0)
    S-->>F: MatchSettled event
    F->>U: Show Claim XP button
    U->>F: Click Claim
    F->>S: claim_xp(match, &mut passport)
    S-->>F: XpClaimed event
    F-->>U: Tier-up animation
